{"tid":365138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙學判囚】香港導演陳嘉上：政府主動製造社會撕裂","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T06:28:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"544fc5e03766536516a58c9ef4b13ab3c8885fe0","tid":365138,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57100214&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57100214%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170819&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqEbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=58dea1a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57100214%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170819&h=50d7e442\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57100214&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170819</a><br />\n<br />\n【雙學判囚】陳嘉上fb撰文：政府主動製造社會撕裂<br />\n即時要聞 <br />\n2017-08-19 11:25:14 HKT<br />\n<br />\n3年前參與重奪公民廣場的雙學三子黃之鋒、羅冠聰及周永康，經律政司覆核刑期後，上訴庭改判三人入獄6至8個月。香港電影導演及編劇陳嘉上在判刑後於fb撰文，指「若法院對以暴力執法的犯罪抱同一態度，我沒有問題。問題是我看到兩種態度，一時強調法律，一時強調包容，因政治立場而異。」並指出「不要再問社會為何撕裂，因為這是政府主動製造的。」<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊<br />\n陳嘉上fb貼文：<br />\n一群年輕的公民因進入了被封閉的公民廣場被判重刑。若法院對以暴力執法的犯罪抱同一態度，我沒有問題。問題是我看到兩種態度，一時強調法律，一時強調包容，因政治立場而異。不要再問社會為何撕裂，因為這是政府主動製造的。有良心的人都無法為你們塗脂抹粉，太醜陋。<br />\n要求再審的是政府，不是嗎？和司法是否獨立無關。在這時候不發聲我過不了自己的關。這判决撕裂社會，對改善社會局面沒有好處。這是我看法。<br />\n<br />\n【網民點講】<br />\nCoco Man：好明顯以強凌弱。<br />\nGary Cheung：一個地方的是否法治，就是看她對待平民跟權貴如何，現在香港就是對平民重刑，對權貴留手。<br />\nBobby Kwok：法官判決獨立是否名存實亡可以討論，但袁國強帶頭政治打壓幾可成事實。<br />\n施仁毅：初審已經判了社會服務令，是政府要求再審，要求重判來殺一儆百，這是政府的選擇，這和司法獨立無關！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170819/large/1503109414_153a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170819%2Flarge%2F1503109414_153a.jpg&h=b56b6c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170819/large/1503109416_1ad1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170819%2Flarge%2F1503109416_1ad1.jpg&h=26dd209c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4c8f94eb9734c73362872c7a1dc5585ea97566e","tid":365138,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波"},{"pid":"05fc548b4b88c26e03ac46fcc726c56332779ecf","tid":365138,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5182fe337f06400de35b545e21544b4c68404bdc","tid":365138,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"根本政府就比你地入<br />\n咁大個機會送上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaab1798ae339c106febef75ee00328e180c4012","tid":365138,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af6ab32fa4826e69c635646617ee405a89b8be8","tid":365138,"uid":36820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"陳嘉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a36835a82f7dfc22fd167a20b943a3ab8dc849","tid":365138,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a35fab0a7d9b85cef44dd5fc9563fe6025450f0","tid":365138,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:22:46.000Z","